NAME
	scroll - file display tool for manual or automatic viewing

SYNOPSIS
	scroll [file]

DESCRIPTION
	scroll is a filter for paging through text one screenful at a time, or automatically scrolling through the text one line 
	at a time

Usage
	Key Inputs:

	space - display the next screenful of text
	enter/return - begin automatically scrolling
		       default speed is 1 line per 2 seconds
	'f' - while automatically scrolling, increases speed at which lines are displayed
	's' - while automatically scrolling, decreases speed at which lines are displayed	
